  "detailed_description": "An abandoned, strange house hidden in the dark forest. Nearby is a barn with unholy energy. Unpleasant hell noise sounds from everywhere. What happened to the family that lived here? Did they create something that should remain forgotten here in the forest? What kind of creature is that? Is that even human? I'll try to find out what's going on here.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Walk around<br></li><li> Find the hidden objects<br></li><li> Solve puzzles<br></li><li> Manage your battery use<br></li><li> Awaken the evil spirit<br></li><li> Fight for your survival</li></ul>",
